data.description: Picture yourself in this very unique and comfortable setting, a Penthouse Suite less than 1 mile from the shores of beautiful Lake Tahoe. The McCloud community in Incline Village has become one of the most sought after locations on the NV side of Tahoe and this luxury Top Floor residence is in a class of it's own! Very few floorplans of this type were ever constructed making this turnkey mountain retreat the ideal getaway you've been waiting for. Storing your ski & beach toys while securing your vehicle indoors is made easy with your private garage directly below the unit. 5 IVGID passes included. Come see the majesty of these Sierra Nevada views from the balcony yourself before this rare opportunity moves on its next owner!
